<view class="container">
  <view class="header">
    <view class="logo">📊</view>
    <view class="title">璇天凤舞的数据助手</view>
  </view>

  <view class="content">
    <view class="card">
      <view class="card-title">核心功能</view>
      <view class="feature-grid">
        <view class="feature-item" bindtap="goToData">
          <text class="feature-icon">📈</text>
          <text class="feature-title">交易数据</text>
        </view>
        <view class="feature-item" bindtap="goToStrategy">
          <text class="feature-icon">🎯</text>
          <text class="feature-title">交易策略</text>
        </view>
        <view class="feature-item" bindtap="goToTools">
          <text class="feature-icon">🔧</text>
          <text class="feature-title">交易工具</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="card">
      <view class="card-title">使用指南</view>
      <view class="guide-list">
        <view class="guide-item">
          <text class="guide-number">1</text>
          <text class="guide-text">浏览「交易数据」，了解不同投资标的数据源</text>
        </view>
        <view class="guide-item">
          <text class="guide-number">2</text>
          <text class="guide-text">查看「交易策略」，了解策略社区和研究报告</text>
        </view>
        <view class="guide-item">
          <text class="guide-number">3</text>
          <text class="guide-text">探索「交易工具」，了解常用交易软件和工具</text>
        </view>
        <view class="guide-item">
          <text class="guide-number">4</text>
          <text class="guide-text">点击官网获取链接，点入详情页获取更多解读</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="footer">
    <text decode="{{true}}">免责声明：本小程序提供的信息仅供参考，不构成投资建议</text>
  </view>
</view>
